            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">Choosing horses in the horse stables of Lishu, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">Shengong Zipan carried [with him] a yellow and white colt </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">Prince Wei seized it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">and Shengong fought over it. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">Prince Wei rose to become the king; </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">Shengong Zipan had an audience with the king, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en">and the king said </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en">"Have you forgotten about that take over (?) in Lishu?" </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">Shengong said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">"I did not know that your majesty would become my lord. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">If I knew that you would be my lord </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en">I would have rather sent it [back] to you." </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en">The king said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en">"I am just teasing you about it, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en">forget about these words. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en">Now that you are serving me, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0062_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en">you must (also) adopt this spirit [of reconciliation]." </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
